    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>No Need for Flowers</i></strong> is an arcade-style scrolling shooter bullet hell game about magic dragon girls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a dragon priestess on a quest to stop a mysterious necromancer from destroying the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/d0c8bf15cee4e01beaa641c200663011.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/d0c8bf15cee4e01beaa641c200663011.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/b246b7838639fcd5bb17aad02f47c6c3.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/b246b7838639fcd5bb17aad02f47c6c3.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skillfully dodge</strong> colorful bullet patterns as you <strong>shoot down hordes of enemies</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/a916ee46200a2f5fc94678e07c9b6155.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/a916ee46200a2f5fc94678e07c9b6155.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> power stars [<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/190e0dc296e9008ab2e43e34d3f209de.webp?t=1763931828\" width=13 height=12 /></span>] to charge up a special attack! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/ceb5f514d681c91f18a7acb104f6c6d1.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=399 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/ceb5f514d681c91f18a7acb104f6c6d1.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight</strong> other dragons in <strong>intense boss battles</strong> that test both your skill and memory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/89c2e05dba416d1ecb75f03e2a91fc8a.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/89c2e05dba416d1ecb75f03e2a91fc8a.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from <strong>3 playable characters</strong>, each with their own <strong>unique</strong> <strong>playstyle and story</strong> <strong>to experience</strong>!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/f8e45fe79ad7de9c03835f64a5354208.apng?t=1763931828\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/f8e45fe79ad7de9c03835f64a5354208.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/9e12ed79866aff3ba0d738b1c9c17c52.webp?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=3 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/f617433b70d3bdbcea0a5f72dd53ed8e.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/f617433b70d3bdbcea0a5f72dd53ed8e.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Experience <strong>7 unique stages</strong>, each with their own gimmicks and bosses to master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Enjoy a beautiful <strong>17-track OST</strong> composed by Princess Sylvysprit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Uncover <strong>a tragic story</strong> <strong>about acceptance</strong> through <strong>expressive characters and dialogue</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Record and re-watch your playthroughs with <strong>replays</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Hone your skills with an <strong>in-depth practice mode</strong> <i>(which hides a few secrets...)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ Learn more about the bosses you've defeated in <strong>an unlockable bestiary</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✿ ... <strong>And more!!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An easy mode, which is perfect for those new to the genre</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/9e12ed79866aff3ba0d738b1c9c17c52.webp?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=3 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/b93ce32d9ca64b50c29a166c4c26a619.apng?t=1763931828\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/b93ce32d9ca64b50c29a166c4c26a619.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/c825cc0db37b4fe015480b8c2c68c1d9.avif?t=1763931828\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras_big/c825cc0db37b4fe015480b8c2c68c1d9.avif?t=1763931828 width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>At the edge of the earth lies a floating island inhabited by <strong>dragons</strong> called <strong>Mallow.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/ba6349e16f379648514dbe0e819a27b6.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/ba6349e16f379648514dbe0e819a27b6.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dragons wield <strong>incredible magic</strong>, capable of bending the universe to their will.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/847e2ed79289157d72fb5b6b3bc6fd16.poster.avif?t=1763931828\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/847e2ed79289157d72fb5b6b3bc6fd16.webm?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337840/extras/847e2ed79289157d72fb5b6b3bc6fd16.mp4?t=1763931828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>But any dragon who uses their magic for evil is sealed away by <strong>a priestess</strong>...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recently, there have been rumors spreading about an evil<strong> necromancer</strong> who is planning to revive a dangerous <strong>monster</strong> at the peak of the mountain. After hearing about this, a lone priestess sets out to stop them.</p>",
